REQ-0010: add openssh-server, so that when booting, it is possible to connect to target
REQ-0020: change security policy on /etc/ssh/sshd_config, so that root Linux accoutn can login on the target. 
  As a result, please launch :


sed -i -e 's/#PermitRootLogin prohibit-password/PermitRootLogin yes/g' /etc/ssh/sshd_config
